Droplet commands is for bootstrapping Digitalocean droplets in Longboat.

Usage:
  boat droplet <command>

Requirements:
  The Digitalocean command line tool must be installed and authenticated:
  https://github.com/digitalocean/doctl/blob/master/README.md

Commands:
  get         Get Droplet info.
  list        List Digitalocean droplets.
  create      Creating new Droplets.

Use "boat droplet <command> -h" for more information about a command.
